1
00:00:25,679 --> 00:00:26,440
You're here.

2
00:01:08,680 --> 00:01:09,280
Right.

3
00:01:10,239 --> 00:01:11,120
First, we find the tail end.

4
00:01:12,400 --> 00:01:13,519
There's one person who's crucial.

5
00:01:13,799 --> 00:01:15,239
That's Wu Chengming,

6
00:01:15,239 --> 00:01:17,040
who got a 55-million loan through Shen Qing and Su Zhuang.

7
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:20,239
Both the Economic Crime Division and Criminal Investigation sent people,

8
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:21,519
but no one has found him.

9
00:01:25,599 --> 00:01:26,879
The problem still lies at the top.

10
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:28,439
You mean...

11
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:31,480
to get Wu Chengming to surface,

12
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:33,680
we have to make Xu Wenwen

13
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:35,680
feel that there's no danger.

14
00:01:37,079 --> 00:01:37,799
Right now,

15
00:01:38,599 --> 00:01:40,040
for Xu Wenwen,

16
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:43,000
the biggest threat

17
00:01:43,480 --> 00:01:44,200
is you.

18
00:01:44,599 --> 00:01:46,159
So she has to eliminate me.

19
00:01:49,959 --> 00:01:50,840
Maybe only when I'm dead

20
00:01:52,359 --> 00:01:53,719
will everything calm down.

21
00:01:54,159 --> 00:01:55,879
And Wu Chengming will naturally surface.

22
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,120
What nonsense are you spouting?

23
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:01,079
I'll just go confront Chief Xing directly.

24
00:02:01,319 --> 00:02:02,400
I don't think Chief Xing has

25
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:03,760
secured evidence of Xu Wenwen's crimes yet.

26
00:02:04,439 --> 00:02:05,959
He's still trying to fix all this.

27
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:09,800
Only by gaining Xu Wenwen's full trust

28
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:12,479
can he dig up evidence of her crimes.

29
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:14,520
What if

30
00:02:15,599 --> 00:02:16,800
you've guessed wrong?

31
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:23,080
I think Chief Xing is a man of strong principles.

32
00:02:23,759 --> 00:02:25,039
He came up from the frontline

33
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:26,639
of Criminal Investigation, fighting his way

34
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:28,800
to the position of Chief of Criminal Investigation.

35
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:31,800
I believe he'll do it.

36
00:02:33,199 --> 00:02:33,840
Otherwise,

37
00:02:36,479 --> 00:02:38,080
he wouldn't have let me go this way.

38
00:02:39,159 --> 00:02:39,960
I see.

39
00:02:41,719 --> 00:02:42,560
That night,

40
00:02:43,639 --> 00:02:46,120
Chief Xing was ready to confess everything.

41
00:02:46,479 --> 00:02:47,439
Who'd have thought Xing Mingliang

42
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,639
would frame you as the murderer.

43
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,039
So only I

44
00:02:52,039 --> 00:02:53,599
can draw out Xu Wenwen's hitman.

45
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:54,840
This is too dangerous.

46
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,560
If something goes wrong,

47
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,080
then it's my fate.

48
00:03:04,439 --> 00:03:05,400
I'll prep a car for you,

49
00:03:06,199 --> 00:03:07,159
to back up your operation.

50
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:10,840
I'm leaving.

51
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:19,439
Brother Wang,

52
00:03:23,319 --> 00:03:24,319
thank you for trusting me.

53
00:03:24,759 --> 00:03:25,319
Hey,

54
00:03:26,319 --> 00:03:27,479
you suddenly becoming

55
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:29,719
someone who says thank you,

56
00:03:30,319 --> 00:03:31,199
I'm really not

57
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:32,919
used to it.

58
00:03:35,439 --> 00:03:36,039
Wait.

59
00:03:39,919 --> 00:03:40,479
Take this.

60
00:04:12,919 --> 00:04:13,639
Are you okay?

61
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:21,600
How is it?

62
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:22,920
Are you alright?

63
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:24,240
I'm fine.

64
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,319
You got here just in time.

65
00:04:27,519 --> 00:04:28,759
Why did you suddenly change your route?

66
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:31,079
I suddenly received a tip.

67
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:33,279
Possible evidence against Xu Wenwen.

68
00:04:35,199 --> 00:04:36,160
I wanted to catch him alive.

69
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:37,360
But now he's dead.

70
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,399
How do we proceed?

71
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:40,759
There's only one way.

72
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:42,399
Turn their plan against them.

73
00:04:43,319 --> 00:04:45,120
You find a way to delay news of the killer's death.

74
00:04:45,959 --> 00:04:46,879
I'll find a way.

75
00:04:46,879 --> 00:04:48,240
To find evidence against Xu Wenwen.

76
00:04:49,879 --> 00:04:51,000
Alright, no problem.

77
00:04:52,319 --> 00:04:52,879
Let's go.

78
00:05:00,079 --> 00:05:01,319
I understand everything you said.

79
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:03,680
I don't believe Comrade Li Kaiyang

80
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:05,240
would do anything that betrays

81
00:05:05,519 --> 00:05:06,839
a police officer's principles.

82
00:05:07,519 --> 00:05:08,160
Right now,

83
00:05:08,439 --> 00:05:10,480
news of his death has hit the media.

84
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:13,600
Nearly all of Fengdu knows about it.

85
00:05:15,519 --> 00:05:17,240
This situation is indeed tricky.

86
00:05:19,759 --> 00:05:20,639
If we now

87
00:05:20,959 --> 00:05:23,360
reveal the truth behind Li Kaiyang's death,

88
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,240
the mastermind behind it

89
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,759
will surely stop everything

90
00:05:26,879 --> 00:05:27,720
and disappear without a trace.

91
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:30,360
Then all our investigative progress

92
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,600
will go down the drain.

93
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,560
I've considered that too.

94
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:35,360
Chief Gao,

95
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:38,160
can we go along with their plan

96
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:39,079
and turn it against them?

97
00:05:39,959 --> 00:05:42,240
First, it'll lower the criminals' guard.

98
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:43,720
Second, it'll buy Li Kaiyang

99
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:45,680
precious time for the investigation.

100
00:05:48,519 --> 00:05:49,600
I agree with your plan.

101
00:05:50,519 --> 00:05:52,199
In the criminals' eyes, Li Kaiyang

102
00:05:52,199 --> 00:05:53,279
is a major threat.

103
00:05:53,439 --> 00:05:54,399
Let them believe

104
00:05:54,639 --> 00:05:56,759
that this thorn has been removed.

105
00:05:57,199 --> 00:05:58,319
They'll definitely let their guard down.

106
00:05:58,839 --> 00:05:59,439
And that

107
00:05:59,759 --> 00:06:01,120
will be our perfect chance

108
00:06:01,639 --> 00:06:03,120
to obtain evidence of their crimes.

109
00:06:03,439 --> 00:06:04,000
Chief Gao,

110
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:07,360
I'll do everything to ensure the operation succeeds.

111
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:08,639
Remember,

112
00:06:09,439 --> 00:06:11,600
not a word of this can leak out.

113
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,560
If word gets out,

114
00:06:14,319 --> 00:06:15,920
not only will Li Kaiyang's life be in danger,

115
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:19,160
our entire operation will fall apart.

116
00:06:31,439 --> 00:06:32,040
Chief Gao,

117
00:06:32,839 --> 00:06:33,720
now,

118
00:06:34,639 --> 00:06:36,560
let me brief you on the Chief Xing matter.

119
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,639
You're here.

120
00:06:52,079 --> 00:06:53,360
The wait just now

121
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:56,199
felt so long.

122
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:00,439
Once the seed of evil is planted in the heart,

123
00:07:00,439 --> 00:07:01,639
it's hard to remove.

124
00:07:02,199 --> 00:07:03,560
If it takes root and sprouts,

125
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:06,480
pulling it out

126
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:08,600
becomes even harder.

127
00:07:10,279 --> 00:07:11,519
You once taught us

128
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:13,600
that when we make mistakes,

129
00:07:14,879 --> 00:07:15,879
we must face them bravely

130
00:07:17,199 --> 00:07:18,120
and correct them sincerely.

131
00:07:19,319 --> 00:07:20,279
It's never too late,

132
00:07:22,279 --> 00:07:25,240
as long as we don't cross the line of the law.

133
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:28,040
I once swore an oath

134
00:07:28,279 --> 00:07:30,399
to defend the honor of the police for life.

135
00:07:31,199 --> 00:07:31,800
For that,

136
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:33,839
I resisted temptation after temptation.

137
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:36,399
But when faced with my own son

138
00:07:36,399 --> 00:07:38,360
committing heinous crimes,

139
00:07:40,879 --> 00:07:42,079
I chose

140
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:43,639
to cover for him.

141
00:07:44,759 --> 00:07:46,720
It led to irreversible consequences.

142
00:07:48,079 --> 00:07:48,720
Chief Xing,

143
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:50,839
if you turn back now,

144
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:54,120
it's not too late.

145
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,439
I hope so.

146
00:08:00,839 --> 00:08:03,079
Your plan gave me an opportunity.

147
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:05,720
It let me gather a lot of

148
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:07,079
key evidence of Xu Wenwen's crimes.

149
00:08:07,439 --> 00:08:08,560
Every time we met,

150
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:10,519
I recorded it with a hidden camera.

151
00:08:16,079 --> 00:08:17,000
Later on,

152
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:18,839
I went to check,

153
00:08:20,199 --> 00:08:21,839
and found that on the corpse's arm,

154
00:08:22,079 --> 00:08:23,120
there was a viper tattoo,

155
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:25,160
the same as the one on the arm of

156
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:27,120
Sun Meng, Xu Wenwen's club manager.

157
00:08:31,519 --> 00:08:32,639
Because of that detail,

158
00:08:33,279 --> 00:08:33,960
I'm certain

159
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:36,360
Xu Wenwen sent someone to kill you.

160
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,639
I will turn myself in.

161
00:08:47,879 --> 00:08:48,559
Promise me,

162
00:08:49,679 --> 00:08:51,279
you must bring her to justice.

163
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:52,960
Yes, sir.

164
00:08:56,639 --> 00:08:57,399
Chief Xing.

165
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:03,039
Chief Xing!

166
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:07,320
Jiang Han,

167
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:09,639
hand me my bag.

168
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:26,360
This...

169
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:29,919
Chief Xing gave this to me before he fell.

170
00:09:32,399 --> 00:09:32,919
Jiang Han.

171
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:34,000
Play it.

172
00:09:42,879 --> 00:09:44,600
You're really framing me here.

173
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:47,600
Pinning such a huge accusation on me,

174
00:09:48,039 --> 00:09:49,480
won't that crush me?

175
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:50,240
Right.

176
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:52,440
You're digging your own grave.

177
00:09:52,759 --> 00:09:53,480
Let me tell you,

178
00:09:53,759 --> 00:09:55,360
don't count on me to clean up your mess anymore.

179
00:09:55,360 --> 00:09:55,919
Chief Xing,

180
00:09:56,039 --> 00:09:57,639
Li Kaiyang's been a detective for so many years,

181
00:09:58,279 --> 00:09:59,840
who knows how many people he's offended.

182
00:10:01,519 --> 00:10:02,759
As long as it wasn't you.

183
00:10:03,399 --> 00:10:04,120
Let me tell you,

184
00:10:04,919 --> 00:10:05,960
once Chief Gao returns from the province,

185
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:07,960
he'll set up a task force right away,

186
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:10,559
mobilizing the city's top officers to crack it.

187
00:10:11,399 --> 00:10:12,679
That's all I can tell you.

188
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:14,200
Chief Xing,

189
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:18,039
we're sailing in the same boat now.

190
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:20,039
If you jump ship

191
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:21,240
before we reach shore,

192
00:10:21,879 --> 00:10:24,159
you could easily drown.

193
00:10:24,720 --> 00:10:27,080
I've long been prepared to drown.

194
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:29,000
Chief Xing, my dear big brother,

195
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:30,960
I'm not worthy of that.

196
00:10:31,879 --> 00:10:32,960
From now on,

197
00:10:33,279 --> 00:10:34,519
you're my big brother.

198
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:36,440
Even if I drown,

199
00:10:36,799 --> 00:10:38,159
I can't let you drown.

200
00:10:40,159 --> 00:10:41,159
If you don't tell the truth,

201
00:10:41,759 --> 00:10:42,720
how can I help you?

202
00:10:43,639 --> 00:10:45,120
It really wasn't me.

203
00:10:56,159 --> 00:10:58,200
I've been a detective my whole life.

204
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:01,320
You think your filthy little tricks

205
00:11:01,559 --> 00:11:03,399
could ever fool me?

206
00:11:05,799 --> 00:11:06,559
Chief Xing.

207
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:09,039
I already told you, it wasn't me.

208
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:10,840
The gun's in your hand.

209
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:12,639
You call the shots.

210
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:16,039
Once this gets exposed,

211
00:11:16,519 --> 00:11:17,720
we're both dead.

212
00:11:18,399 --> 00:11:20,519
So I might as well get rid of you,

213
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:22,000
you menace, right now.

214
00:11:23,279 --> 00:11:24,080
Chief Xing.

215
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,679
Why bother with all this?

216
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:29,399
Our biggest obstacle is already gone.

217
00:11:30,039 --> 00:11:32,360
No one will ever know about us.

218
00:11:32,679 --> 00:11:34,960
I despise scheming people the most.

219
00:11:37,879 --> 00:11:38,639
Since

220
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:40,600
you've decided to board my ship,

221
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:43,639
I'll be completely open with you.

222
00:11:44,279 --> 00:11:45,639
Everything I've done

223
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:49,240
has been for you and your own son.

224
00:11:49,399 --> 00:11:50,759
I don't have a bastard son like that.

225
00:11:52,799 --> 00:11:54,840
Brother, even a tiger won't eat its young.

226
00:11:55,679 --> 00:11:58,559
You've spent years on the force,

227
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:02,080
seeing all the good and evil in this world.

228
00:12:02,759 --> 00:12:04,159
But have you ever considered

229
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:05,960
that sometimes

230
00:12:06,279 --> 00:12:08,039
the line between black and white

231
00:12:08,519 --> 00:12:10,799
isn't really that clear-cut?

232
00:12:12,559 --> 00:12:13,759
From what I know,

233
00:12:13,919 --> 00:12:16,639
plenty of people have tried to buy you off.

234
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:18,240
I'll be blunt, even if you don't like it.

235
00:12:18,799 --> 00:12:20,080
I think you're a fool.

236
00:12:20,799 --> 00:12:23,120
You've never tasted the power of money.

237
00:12:23,799 --> 00:12:26,679
It's the master key that opens every door.

238
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:28,080
With money,

239
00:12:28,639 --> 00:12:30,000
anything you want

240
00:12:30,639 --> 00:12:31,799
is within your grasp.

241
00:12:33,159 --> 00:12:33,919
Look at you.

242
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:37,240
You gave most of your life to the police.

243
00:12:37,720 --> 00:12:38,879
And what did you get in the end?

244
00:12:39,159 --> 00:12:41,480
But it'd be different with me.

245
00:12:42,039 --> 00:12:46,039
Any one of these is a year's salary for you.

246
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:48,960
I warned you,

247
00:12:49,759 --> 00:12:50,919
don't touch Li Kaiyang.

248
00:12:51,399 --> 00:12:53,240
Killing the deputy chief of Major Crimes

249
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:54,679
is an enormous matter.

250
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:57,759
I'm afraid you won't live to spend that money.

251
00:12:58,519 --> 00:12:59,279
That's why

252
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:01,240
I'm counting on you, brother.

253
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:03,639
I've already worked out the story.

254
00:13:04,399 --> 00:13:06,360
Li Kaiyang took dirty money from Su Zhuang,

255
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:07,759
hired a hitman,

256
00:13:08,039 --> 00:13:09,559
and worked together to silence witnesses.

257
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:12,799
They fell out over splitting the loot.

258
00:13:13,759 --> 00:13:14,879
This story,

259
00:13:16,120 --> 00:13:17,080
isn't it perfect?

260
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:20,720
It's a well-crafted story.

261
00:13:21,039 --> 00:13:22,360
I'm just afraid no one will buy it.

262
00:13:23,919 --> 00:13:24,960
Don't worry.

263
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:28,200
I had someone wire over two million

264
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:29,440
from overseas to Li Kaiyang's account.

265
00:13:30,360 --> 00:13:31,240
All you have to do

266
00:13:31,559 --> 00:13:33,360
is send someone to investigate.

267
00:13:36,840 --> 00:13:38,039
This footage is crucial,

268
00:13:38,759 --> 00:13:41,559
but it can't fully nail Xu Wenwen's crimes.

269
00:13:42,399 --> 00:13:43,399
We have to find

270
00:13:43,840 --> 00:13:45,039
irrefutable hard evidence.

271
00:13:48,759 --> 00:13:50,080
This is Shen Qing's pet dog.

272
00:13:50,639 --> 00:13:52,120
We found this inside its collar tag.

273
00:13:52,840 --> 00:13:53,759
I've read the contents.

274
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:57,919
It's all the hidden accounts of Xu Wenwen

275
00:13:57,919 --> 00:14:00,159
and Su Zhuang's loan fraud cases over the years.

276
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:03,799
This evidence is incredibly important.

277
00:14:04,080 --> 00:14:05,080
There's something even more important.

278
00:14:11,759 --> 00:14:13,159
This is the notebook Big Liu left behind.

279
00:14:13,320 --> 00:14:14,320
He hid this notebook

280
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:17,440
behind his daughter's honor student certificate.

281
00:14:18,960 --> 00:14:19,639
Chief Gao,

282
00:14:25,879 --> 00:14:27,360
Sun Meng gave me 300,000.

283
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:29,200
She's the personal assistant

284
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:30,639
to Xu Wenwen, chairwoman of Jingwen Group.

285
00:14:30,840 --> 00:14:33,159
She told me to shoot Ma Shijiang dead during the arrest.

286
00:14:33,639 --> 00:14:35,120
The reason I didn't refuse

287
00:14:35,759 --> 00:14:37,759
is because Ma Shijiang deserved to die anyway.

288
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:40,200
And Yaya needed the money for life-saving surgery.

289
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:41,919
But what I never expected

290
00:14:42,320 --> 00:14:43,840
was that it would get Captain Zhao killed.

291
00:14:45,240 --> 00:14:46,120
Captain Zhao, listen to me.

292
00:14:47,519 --> 00:14:48,720
I didn't rape Ruolan.

293
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:52,279
You animal!

294
00:14:52,279 --> 00:14:54,080
You still dare to deny it?

295
00:14:54,559 --> 00:14:55,360
It really wasn't me.

296
00:14:55,639 --> 00:14:56,240
It wasn't.

297
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:58,360
If you don't believe me, listen to this recording.

298
00:15:06,240 --> 00:15:06,840
Big Liu!

299
00:15:07,200 --> 00:15:07,840
What are you doing?

300
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:08,879
Who told you to shoot?

301
00:15:09,240 --> 00:15:09,840
Captain Zhao,

302
00:15:10,240 --> 00:15:11,759
Ma Shijiang is a bastard.

303
00:15:12,080 --> 00:15:13,039
He had to die.

304
00:15:13,399 --> 00:15:15,159
If he committed a crime, the law would judge him.

305
00:15:15,279 --> 00:15:16,919
We can't take justice into our own hands.

306
00:15:17,840 --> 00:15:18,879
Captain Zhao, watch out!

307
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:20,759
Captain Zhao!

308
00:15:21,240 --> 00:15:21,960
Captain Zhao!

309
00:15:23,799 --> 00:15:24,840
Stop the act.

310
00:15:24,960 --> 00:15:26,399
My aunt sent you to save me, didn't she?

311
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:27,919
Captain Zhao,

312
00:15:33,120 --> 00:15:34,080
cover me so I can escape!

313
00:15:39,720 --> 00:15:40,360
Captain Zhao!

314
00:15:43,080 --> 00:15:43,759
Ruolan,

315
00:15:44,639 --> 00:15:46,600
it was Xing Mingliang.

316
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:48,559
That scumbag.

317
00:15:49,480 --> 00:15:50,039
Captain Zhao!

318
00:15:50,639 --> 00:15:51,360
Captain Zhao!

319
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:00,519
Captain Zhao!

320
00:16:00,879 --> 00:16:01,480
Captain Zhao!

321
00:16:11,799 --> 00:16:12,399
Officers,

322
00:16:12,519 --> 00:16:14,759
after countless days and nights of struggle,

323
00:16:14,960 --> 00:16:16,519
and the lives sacrificed by our comrades,

324
00:16:16,840 --> 00:16:18,559
we have now firmly secured

325
00:16:18,919 --> 00:16:20,200
solid evidence of Xu Wenwen's crimes.

326
00:16:20,879 --> 00:16:21,480
I hereby declare

327
00:16:22,080 --> 00:16:23,279
that we will arrest her

328
00:16:23,679 --> 00:16:26,159
and bring this mastermind to justice.

329
00:16:26,480 --> 00:16:27,000
In addition,

330
00:16:27,360 --> 00:16:29,120
Criminal Investigation and the Economic Crime Division will fully cooperate

331
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:32,080
to apprehend everyone connected to Xu Wenwen's case,

332
00:16:32,360 --> 00:16:33,639
every last one of them.

333
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:36,320
Let the light of justice shine across Fengdu.

334
00:16:38,559 --> 00:16:40,120
We will complete the mission!

335
00:16:40,320 --> 00:16:41,960
We will complete the mission!

336
00:16:59,159 --> 00:17:00,440
Why do you keep staring at me?

337
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:02,480
Is there something on my face?

338
00:17:02,679 --> 00:17:03,639
Just focus on driving.

339
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:06,039
Master.

340
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:08,759
I think you owe me an apology.

341
00:17:09,240 --> 00:17:09,880
An apology?

342
00:17:10,799 --> 00:17:11,559
For what?

343
00:17:12,200 --> 00:17:14,039
I saved you from that crossbow.

344
00:17:14,160 --> 00:17:15,599
And I still owe you an apology?

345
00:17:16,799 --> 00:17:17,559
That's not it.

346
00:17:18,079 --> 00:17:19,000
You faked your death.

347
00:17:19,759 --> 00:17:22,160
Captain Wang and Chief Gao both knew.

348
00:17:22,359 --> 00:17:23,279
I was the only one left out.

349
00:17:24,680 --> 00:17:26,400
Do you even consider me a brother?

350
00:17:26,759 --> 00:17:27,799
I'm your master.

351
00:17:28,920 --> 00:17:29,880
When there's danger like this,

352
00:17:30,799 --> 00:17:31,960
of course the master takes the risk.

353
00:17:36,480 --> 00:17:37,599
Fine, don't tell anyone else,

354
00:17:37,599 --> 00:17:38,880
but you should've told me.

355
00:17:38,880 --> 00:17:40,039
I'm your apprentice.

356
00:17:40,599 --> 00:17:42,920
I guess an apprentice's tears mean nothing.

357
00:17:45,400 --> 00:17:45,960
Fine.

358
00:17:46,440 --> 00:17:48,000
Next time there's danger like this,

359
00:17:48,599 --> 00:17:49,440
you go in my place, alright?

360
00:17:50,039 --> 00:17:50,599
Huh?
